# 🤖 NOVA – AI Desktop Assistant

> **A futuristic desktop AI assistant inspired by J.A.R.V.I.S. from Iron Man.**

NOVA is a Python-powered desktop AI assistant designed to provide a modern, intelligent, and interactive desktop experience. It combines voice recognition, local AI, desktop automation, and a futuristic user interface into a single application.

---

# ✨ Features

### 🧠 AI Intelligence

* Local AI powered by **Ollama**
* Natural language conversations
* Context-aware responses
* Offline AI support
* Fast response time

### 🎤 Voice Assistant

* Voice recognition
* Text-to-speech responses
* Clap-to-wake functionality
* Hands-free interaction
* Custom assistant personality

### 💻 Desktop Automation

* Launch desktop applications
* Open websites
* Search Google
* Search YouTube
* Take screenshots
* Control system volume
* Type text automatically
* System information monitoring

### 🗂 Memory System

* Save notes
* Recall previous notes
* Personalized interactions

### 🎨 Modern Interface

* Futuristic HUD-inspired design
* Animated AI core
* Dark cyber-themed UI
* Smooth chat interface
* Responsive layout

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

## Programming Language

* Python 3.11+

## AI

* Ollama
* Llama 3.2

## GUI

* PyQt6

## Voice

* SpeechRecognition
* pyttsx3

## Automation

* PyAutoGUI
* psutil

## Audio

* sounddevice
* NumPy

